data.description: Beautiful new construction in Fox Creek Country Club Subdivision, which surrounds the highly acclaimed Arnold Palmer Signature Golf Course in Bloomington, The Den!  This home features a traditional floor plan with 4 bedroom/2.5 baths, 3-car garage and NO Backyard Neighbors.  Amazing price for the area.
data.whatILove: Love the open floor plan and no backyard neighbors. Low traffic tucked way back on Carrington. Tremendous price on new construction for Fox Creek!
